    26  
    27  Use overlays after selecting any applicable package/plugin archetype:
    28  
    29  | Overlay             | Use                                             
|
    30  | ------------------- | 
-------------------------------------------------------------------- |
    31  | `SCOPE-frontend.md` | Fresh, UI, route, browser, or visual workflow 
work                   |
    32  | `SCOPE-service.md`  | `services/`, API handler, background runtime, or
Aspire service work |
    33  | `SCOPE-docs.md`     | RFC, README, knowledge base, run artifact, or 
doctrine-facing docs   |
    34  
    35  ## Required Output in Plans
    36  
